subject: Soccer
NCAA Soccer Championships
organizations: Virginia Polytechnic Institute and State University
lead_paragraph: Jamia Fields led Florida State to the N.C.A.A. Women’s College Cup final in Cary, N.C., scoring twice in the second half in the Seminoles’ 3-2 win over Virginia Tech.
snippet: Jamia Fields led Florida State to the N.C.A.A. Women’s College Cup final in Cary, N.C., scoring twice in the second half in the Seminoles’ 3-2 win over Virginia Tech.
